div.div: When the disaster called "Portal Impact" ended it left Park Hyun-So to pick up the pieces after his parents' death and his younger brother was left in a deep coma. Years later after suffering hardships and massively in debt due to his brother's hospital bills, Hyun-Soo meets Chung-Yeong, a martial artist from another world! Chung-Yeong, a murim martial master who had been astral projecting could not return to his body, when a portal appeared and sucked him in, taking him to modern Korea. After months not being able to interact with anyone Chung-Yeong out of boredom takes on Hyun-Soo as his student and begins to teach him martial arts…

Lee Hojae had given up his life as a pro gamer, until one day he received a mysterious message: “Congratulations! You’ve been invited to the Tutorial World.” Intrigued, he enters the game and confidently chooses “hell” difficulty, but soon learns that he is trapped there. With a mere 0.01% survival rate, Hojae must somehow overcome the game’s agonizing challenges to figure out the real reason he was invited. This tutorial may be tough, but its secrets are what’s truly hellacious. (Source: Tapas)
